Package oracle.apps.fnd.applcore.dt.patterns.utils

Generic utility classes.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
ApplicationsTableUtils General methods for Applications Table that do not otherwise fit anywhere.
ApplicationsTreeUtils General methods for Applications Tree that do not otherwise fit anywhere.
ApplicationsUIUtils Common utility class.
ContextUtils This class contains various utilities for conversion between Contexts.
DataControlUtils DataControlUtils is a utility file that contains methods determine attributes on the selected Data Source.
DomAttribute An immutable value object representing an Attribute pertaining to a DOM Node.
DomUtils This class contins various xml dom utilities.
JSFUniqueIdGenerator This class decorates the ADFDesignTimeContext.generateUniqueIdForView(baseId) method for the case where we are generating complex trees containing similar elements that require unique ids.
MasterDetailElementHolder This class acts as a simple immutable bean to point into a constructed Dom subtreerepresenting an fnd:applicationsMasterDetail.
PopupElementHolder This class acts as a simple immutable bean to point into a constructed Dom subtreerepresenting an fnd:applicationsPopup.
TableElementHolder This class acts as a simple immutable bean to point into a constructed Dom subtree representing an fnd:applicationsTable.
TreeElementHolder This class acts as a simple immutable bean to point into a constructed Dom subtree representing an fnd:applicationsTree.
TreeTableElementHolder This class acts as a simple immutable bean to point into a constructed Dom subtree representing an fnd:applicationsTreeTable.
TypeUtils Various utilities for Types.
